g.text: 2. Receive notification about the result of job requests
3. Counts the event and stores the result in the distributed cache for one hour.
4. At each schedule, it generates a report containing two types of information:
1. The general count, that is, from when the service is active until now.
2. A snippet of the last five minutes
5. Stores the report in the cache
6. Publish a notification about monitoring report in Kafka
